01:43:01.680 --> 01:43:04.640
Better educated parents are more likely to have better jobs

01:43:04.640 --> 01:43:07.200
and therefore less likely to have children in poverty.

01:43:07.200 --> 01:43:08.960
This is rather straightforward.

01:43:08.960 --> 01:43:11.280
