01:43:11.280 --> 01:43:13.840
A family with a particular income and living space

01:43:13.840 --> 01:43:16.720
stretched to take care of six children, say,

01:43:16.720 --> 01:43:20.160
is gonna have a harder time than a family with the same income and living space

01:43:20.160 --> 01:43:22.480
but only one child to take care of.

01:43:22.480 --> 01:43:24.960
