01:43:52.640 --> 01:43:55.760
the average crime rate, the unemployment rate,

01:43:55.760 --> 01:43:59.600
that can be very important for determining one's chance of being in poverty.

01:43:59.600 --> 01:44:01.200
Seems fairly obvious to mention,

01:44:01.200 --> 01:44:03.920
but you're gonna have an easier time finding an income

01:44:03.920 --> 01:44:07.680
in an area with many jobs than an area with few jobs.

