To be fair, sometimes they do add other factors to consider,

01:50:33.360 --> 01:50:39.360
but again, only when they personally, subjectively, decide those factors are important.

01:50:39.360 --> 01:50:44.160
All their comparisons between IQ and SES that inform their later policy proposals

01:50:44.160 --> 01:50:47.440
are based upon this calculated decision to not consider

01:50:47.440 --> 01:50:50.400
the full range of relevant environmental factors.

01:50:50.400 --> 01:50:54.480
And there's two other important points that we have to keep in mind here.

