So at some point, different designated racial groups diverged from one another

01:59:55.280 --> 01:59:59.760
and developed different traits according to some sort of trade-off system.

01:59:59.760 --> 02:00:02.560
So it's like a computer game where you have limited points

02:00:02.560 --> 02:00:04.240
to put into your starting stats,

02:00:04.240 --> 02:00:08.640
